        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5652",
        "content": "why did Achilles and Hector hew each other up with vast blows of their lances? Because Helen allowed Paris to take her garter.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5652_19215_000026_000029",
