        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5652",
        "content": "But, in sooth! the stomach is an agreeable beast which demands its due, and which wants to have its wedding also.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5652_19215_000026_000038",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5652/19215/5652_19215_000026_000038.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5652",
        "content": "People had no straps to their boots, they had no boots.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5652_19215_000026_000042",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5652/19215/5652_19215_000026_000042.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5652",
        "content": "One of the sides of that century was delicate, the other was magnificent; and by the green cabbages! people amused themselves. To day, people are serious.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5652_19215_000026_000046",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5652/19215/5652_19215_000026_000046.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5652",
        "content": "Since the revolution, everything, including the ballet dancers, has had its trousers; a mountebank dancer must be grave; your rigadoons are doctrinarian.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
