        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5652",
        "content": "While the grandfather, in full lyrical effusion, was listening to himself, Cosette and Marius grew intoxicated as they gazed freely at each other.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
