        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5652",
        "content": "Marius returned, Marius brought back bleeding, Marius brought back from a barricade, Marius dead, then living, Marius reconciled, Marius betrothed, Marius wedding a poor girl, Marius wedding a millionairess.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
