        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5652",
        "content": "But from such a causal point of view, we should not underestimate the manifold good which can come from the causal effect of religious and ethical ideas.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
